# 1. Add to INSTALLED_APPS in settings.py
INSTALLED_APPS = [
    # ... other apps
    'notifications',
]

# 2. Include URLs in main urls.py
from django.urls import path, include

urlpatterns = [
    # ... other urls
    path('api/notifications/', include('notifications.urls')),
]

# 3. Run migrations
python manage.py makemigrations notifications
python manage.py migrate

# 4. Create default notification templates
python manage.py create_notification_templates

# 5. (Optional) Create superuser if not exists
python manage.py createsuperuser
```

## ðŸŽ¯ **API Endpoints:**
```
# Notifications
GET    /api/notifications/notifications/                  - List all notifications
POST   /api/notifications/notifications/                  - Create notification
GET    /api/notifications/notifications/{id}/             - Get notification
POST   /api/notifications/notifications/{id}/mark_as_read/
POST   /api/notifications/notifications/{id}/mark_as_unread/
POST   /api/notifications/notifications/{id}/archive/
POST   /api/notifications/notifications/mark_all_as_read/
POST   /api/notifications/notifications/mark_multiple_as_read/
DELETE /api/notifications/notifications/clear_all/
GET    /api/notifications/notifications/unread/
GET    /api/notifications/notifications/recent/
GET    /api/notifications/notifications/stats/

# Preferences
GET    /api/notifications/preferences/my_preferences/
PATCH  /api/notifications/preferences/update_preferences/

# Devices
GET    /api/notifications/devices/                        - List devices
POST   /api/notifications/devices/                        - Register device
POST   /api/notifications/devices/{id}/deactivate/

# Templates
GET    /api/notifications/templates/                      - List templates

# Utility Endpoints
POST   /api/notifications/send/                           - Send notification
POST   /api/notifications/send-bulk/                      - Send bulk
POST   /api/notifications/send-template/                  - Send from template
GET    /api/notifications/count/                          - Get unread count
GET    /api/notifications/summary/                        - Get summary
